1
00:01:29,344 --> 00:01:34,500
=City of Streamer=

2
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:37,100
=Episode 32=

3
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:39,519
Father.

4
00:01:45,075 --> 00:01:45,715
Father?

5
00:02:58,925 --> 00:03:00,825
There you are, Miss Feng.

6
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:02,759
Your brother called earlier.

7
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,080
Don't forget to call him back.

8
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,150
Sure. Thanks.

9
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,825
Shixun, it's me.

10
00:03:30,215 --> 00:03:31,054
Did you just get off work?

11
00:03:31,655 --> 00:03:33,135
My class finished hours ago.

12
00:03:33,135 --> 00:03:34,575
The snow was too heavy,

13
00:03:34,614 --> 00:03:36,575
so I went to the café to read.

14
00:03:37,495 --> 00:03:38,694
How are Mother and Father?

15
00:03:39,614 --> 00:03:41,200
They're good.

16
00:03:42,125 --> 00:03:43,885
The new drug

17
00:03:43,885 --> 00:03:45,004
is curing Father's lungs.

18
00:03:45,004 --> 00:03:46,444
His fever is gone.

19
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:47,960
Now,

20
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,800
he and Mother would like to
go to the country retreat,

21
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,080
but I have concerns.

22
00:03:51,425 --> 00:03:53,465
It's quiet and peaceful there

23
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,440
but too far away from the hospital.

24
00:03:55,679 --> 00:03:57,325
If anything happens,

25
00:03:57,325 --> 00:03:58,400
no one is there to help them, right?

26
00:03:58,475 --> 00:03:59,150
Yes.

27
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:00,669
I agree with you on that.

28
00:04:01,025 --> 00:04:03,360
But with me here in Peking

29
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,360
and you at work most of the time,

30
00:04:05,559 --> 00:04:07,725
they must feel lonely.

31
00:04:08,075 --> 00:04:08,875
Shixun,

32
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:11,360
they'll feel better if you get married.

33
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,399
We're talking about their condition.

34
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,500
Don't make it about me.

35
00:04:16,425 --> 00:04:17,239
By the way,

36
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:19,340
is it cold in Peking?

37
00:04:19,625 --> 00:04:20,720
Do you feel uncomfortable there?

38
00:04:21,075 --> 00:04:22,556
The stove inside

39
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,950
makes the room pretty warm.

40
00:04:25,850 --> 00:04:26,649
Shixun,

41
00:04:27,375 --> 00:04:28,775
I miss you all.

42
00:04:29,975 --> 00:04:31,056
Me too.

43
00:04:33,425 --> 00:04:35,279
I read in the paper

44
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:37,239
that Rong Dingkun is out of his coma,

45
00:04:37,239 --> 00:04:38,480
but paralyzed.

46
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,440
That's karma.

47
00:04:41,075 --> 00:04:42,079
But even so,

48
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,519
he has enough money

49
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:45,239
and people to attend to his needs.

50
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,920
He won't suffer at all.

51
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:48,880
For a proud

52
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,799
dictator like him,

53
00:04:50,275 --> 00:04:51,514
paralysis

54
00:04:51,514 --> 00:04:53,234
is probably worse than death.

55
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,450
As far as I know,

56
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:57,690
none of his women

57
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:59,399
truly cares about him.

58
00:04:59,975 --> 00:05:01,295
They won't

59
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,760
fall over themselves like before

60
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,975
to impress a good-for-nothing.

61
00:05:05,125 --> 00:05:06,406
The worst is yet to come.

62
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:09,925
Oh, Shizhen.

63
00:05:09,925 --> 00:05:11,000
(New Head of the Rong Family
Rong Jiashang)

64
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,689
(Cut the Ribbon at Wenchunli Yesterday)
Are you still in touch

65
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,839
with Rong Jiashang?

66
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,839
Not anymore.

67
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,625
After I lied to him,

68
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,160
I just hoped he wouldn't get back at me.

69
00:05:24,559 --> 00:05:25,320
Why do you think

70
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,839
I moved to Peking?

71
00:05:28,225 --> 00:05:29,839
Why did you bring him up anyway?

72
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,400
Just checking.

73
00:05:32,075 --> 00:05:34,000
Look, let me know

74
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,125
if he comes at you.

75
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,279
Even if he doesn't,

76
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,319
stay away from him.

77
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,959
Don't mess with

78
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:41,271
those rich brats.

79
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,075
I know.

80
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:46,975
One more thing.

81
00:05:47,799 --> 00:05:49,320
Tell Concubine Sun

82
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,650
that I ran into her sister here.

83
00:05:52,025 --> 00:05:54,585
Shaoqing is doing fine.

84
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:56,730
She'll receive her letter soon.

85
00:05:56,775 --> 00:05:57,600
Really?

86
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,220
Got it. That's great.

87
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,541
She's having a rough time

88
00:06:02,650 --> 00:06:04,000
when her son

89
00:06:04,799 --> 00:06:06,225
is having a fever.

90
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,650
She might be able to

91
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,625
take comfort from her sister's words.

92
00:06:09,625 --> 00:06:10,250
I hope so.

93
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,000
Your name is put on the envelope.

94
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,625
Don't forget to pick it up for her.

95
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:14,880
Sure, I will.

96
00:06:15,425 --> 00:06:17,559
And don't drain yourself, you know.

97
00:06:18,119 --> 00:06:19,500
I won't. Take care of yourself, too.

98
00:06:35,825 --> 00:06:37,000
Miss Feng,

99
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:39,230
your boyfriend is here.

100
00:06:39,230 --> 00:06:41,519
He's waiting for you outside.

101
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:42,519
Thanks.

102
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,559
You're welcome.

103
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,880
Shizhen,

104
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,920
nice to

105
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:10,470
meet you again.

106
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:21,399
You didn't come all the way to the north

107
00:07:22,125 --> 00:07:24,320
to buy me coffee, did you?

108
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,109
Just get to the point.

109
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:28,650
No need to waste

110
00:07:29,175 --> 00:07:30,350
each other's time.

111
00:07:31,425 --> 00:07:32,586
It's nothing important.

112
00:07:34,875 --> 00:07:37,116
I saw Rong Jiashang

113
00:07:37,559 --> 00:07:38,875
at the Mayor's ball yesterday.

114
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,861
Although his fiancée left him,

115
00:07:42,239 --> 00:07:44,559
more girls were eager to

116
00:07:44,559 --> 00:07:45,839
take her place.

117
00:07:46,525 --> 00:07:49,239
Among them, Miss Hashimoto

118
00:07:49,239 --> 00:07:51,998
is more likely to win.

119
00:07:54,425 --> 00:07:55,600
As far as I know,

120
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:57,689
he's still in charge

121
00:07:58,075 --> 00:07:59,300
despite the fact that

122
00:08:00,525 --> 00:08:02,359
his father has woken up.

123
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:05,279
That scene you made

124
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,599
actually facilitated his succession.

125
00:08:08,275 --> 00:08:09,596
You must

126
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,239
feel frustrated.

127
00:08:16,125 --> 00:08:18,206
Rong Jiashang

128
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,100
has made you more attractive indeed.

129
00:08:21,575 --> 00:08:22,950
Clearly, women can't grow

130
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,911
without men.

131
00:08:26,075 --> 00:08:28,425
I suppose you didn't come all the way

132
00:08:28,625 --> 00:08:29,720
from Shanghai

133
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,160
to pry into my love life.

134
00:08:34,875 --> 00:08:36,320
Rong Jiashang said

135
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,919
he hadn't found your birth father,

136
00:08:38,325 --> 00:08:40,119
didn't he?

137
00:08:42,425 --> 00:08:43,320
And?

138
00:08:43,575 --> 00:08:44,320
Do you believe him?

139
00:08:45,775 --> 00:08:46,840
Since when did you become

140
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,359
so curious about my lineage, Mr. Meng?

141
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,501
Miss Hashimoto

142
00:08:52,825 --> 00:08:54,265
has gone to great lengths

143
00:08:54,675 --> 00:08:56,035
to win Rong Jiashang over.

144
00:08:57,175 --> 00:08:58,520
She paid the newspaper

145
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,320
to disclose Miss Du's affair

146
00:09:00,475 --> 00:09:02,995
and scared Yang Xiucheng away.

147
00:09:04,075 --> 00:09:06,195
Didn't she play right into your hands

148
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:09,751
as you meant to recruit him long ago?

149
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,520
Now that he's down,

150
00:09:11,650 --> 00:09:12,960
you can help him

151
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,000
get back on his feet.

152
00:09:14,575 --> 00:09:16,176
As sophisticated

153
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,760
and selfish as he is,

154
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,400
he's a coward.

155
00:09:20,025 --> 00:09:22,200
He'll yield to power.

156
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,359
You're right about him.

157
00:09:25,125 --> 00:09:26,605
That man

158
00:09:26,775 --> 00:09:28,215
isn't too stupid.

159
00:09:28,215 --> 00:09:29,455
He gave up tons of information,

160
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,000
including your origins,

161
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:34,130
which is

162
00:09:34,475 --> 00:09:36,754
shocking.

163
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,280
After Yang Xiucheng

164
00:09:39,675 --> 00:09:41,675
hooked up with Miss Du,

165
00:09:42,225 --> 00:09:43,650
he started to have people

166
00:09:43,825 --> 00:09:45,119
watch Rong Jiashang's every move

167
00:09:45,475 --> 00:09:47,636
in case he found out about the affair.

168
00:09:48,175 --> 00:09:49,775
When Rong Jiashang had his assistant

169
00:09:49,775 --> 00:09:51,095
dig into your background,

170
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:52,679
he found out about it

171
00:09:52,725 --> 00:09:54,175
and followed his step.

172
00:09:54,650 --> 00:09:56,330
They discovered a photo

173
00:09:56,950 --> 00:09:59,700
and Yang Xiucheng made a copy of it.

174
00:10:28,119 --> 00:10:29,450
When was this photo taken?

175
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,719
A long time ago.

176
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:33,404
The owner of the photo

177
00:10:33,599 --> 00:10:35,000
is said to be your aunt,

178
00:10:35,125 --> 00:10:36,725
which is confirmed by Rong Jiashang.

179
00:10:36,950 --> 00:10:38,799
The couple in the photo is Rong Dingkun

180
00:10:38,825 --> 00:10:40,919
and his wife

181
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,080
who gave birth

182
00:10:42,425 --> 00:10:43,625
to you.

183
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,175
After she died

184
00:10:47,175 --> 00:10:48,200
of illness,

185
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,125
Rong Dingkun married Ms. Tang

186
00:10:49,225 --> 00:10:50,719
who was Rong Jiashang's mother.

187
00:10:51,275 --> 00:10:52,915
If it's true that woman in the photo

188
00:10:52,915 --> 00:10:54,450
was your birth mother,

189
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,799
you'd be

190
00:10:57,175 --> 00:10:58,640
a Rong,

191
00:10:58,875 --> 00:11:00,150
the eldest daughter

192
00:11:00,239 --> 00:11:01,325
of Rong Dingkun.

193
00:11:01,325 --> 00:11:02,300
Enough!

194
00:11:09,275 --> 00:11:10,039
Mr. Meng,

195
00:11:10,719 --> 00:11:12,250
everything you say without evidence,

196
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,100
solid evidence, is mere speculation.

197
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,081
You expect me to believe

198
00:11:16,125 --> 00:11:17,925
that man is my father

199
00:11:18,425 --> 00:11:20,024
based on a blurry photo

200
00:11:20,675 --> 00:11:22,000
and a story

201
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,440
you made up?

202
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:26,570
I don't care how many wives
Rong Dingkun has had.

203
00:11:26,570 --> 00:11:28,450
He cannot be my father.

204
00:11:29,599 --> 00:11:31,359
You think you know everything,

205
00:11:31,425 --> 00:11:32,466
but

206
00:11:32,466 --> 00:11:33,640
there's still a lot about me

207
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,880
that you don't know.

208
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,400
What do you mean?

209
00:11:42,375 --> 00:11:43,520
That the one

210
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:46,949
who tried to kill you and your mother

211
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,350
was your father Rong Dingkun?

212
00:11:57,075 --> 00:11:58,400
Don't give me that look.

213
00:11:58,725 --> 00:12:00,159
No one is stalking you.

214
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:02,200
It's just my theory

215
00:12:02,825 --> 00:12:04,624
based on facts.

216
00:12:05,050 --> 00:12:06,525
What else do you know?

217
00:12:07,675 --> 00:12:09,080
The time of death

218
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,280
of Rong Dingkun's first wife

219
00:12:11,625 --> 00:12:12,650
and children

220
00:12:13,575 --> 00:12:15,719
matches that of your mother's death

221
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:17,125
and you

222
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,961
being adopted by the Fengs.

223
00:12:19,625 --> 00:12:21,275
Young as you were,

224
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:23,039
I believe

225
00:12:23,450 --> 00:12:24,775
you could remember things.

226
00:12:25,125 --> 00:12:27,406
You knew the one after you
and your mother's life

227
00:12:27,775 --> 00:12:29,225
was your father,

228
00:12:29,625 --> 00:12:31,175
in this case, Rong Dingkun.

229
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:40,530
You're really selling it.

230
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:43,891
What about my missing younger brother?

231
00:12:45,875 --> 00:12:47,714
Don't tell me that's Rong Jiashang.

232
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:52,280
His age doesn't match.

233
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:55,250
That said,

234
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:56,520
Rong Dingkun

235
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:58,640
cares a lot about his sons.

236
00:12:58,750 --> 00:13:01,469
He might've kept that boy
somewhere else.

237
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,691
As convincing as it sounds,

238
00:13:04,175 --> 00:13:06,815
it's still your assumption

239
00:13:07,025 --> 00:13:08,575
unless Rong Dingkun says it's true.

240
00:13:09,025 --> 00:13:10,200
No way are

241
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:12,215
Rong Jiashang and I related!

242
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:24,660
What else do you have to say?

243
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,799
I came

244
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:28,760
in person

245
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,799
to tell you this

246
00:13:30,075 --> 00:13:31,195
not to mock you.

247
00:13:32,125 --> 00:13:34,080
Rong Dingkun is not my father!

248
00:13:35,650 --> 00:13:37,371
If you don't believe what I said,

249
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:38,830
let's go back to Shanghai

250
00:13:38,830 --> 00:13:39,791
and ask your aunt

251
00:13:39,791 --> 00:13:40,830
about the whole truth.

252
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,430
You sent me here,

253
00:13:45,675 --> 00:13:47,400
and now, you want me back.

254
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,000
Meng Xu'an, what's your game?

255
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,120
There's none.

256
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,880
I just feel that

257
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:53,900
you deserve to know the truth.

258
00:13:56,025 --> 00:13:58,025
What I deserve is peace.

259
00:13:59,100 --> 00:14:01,460
I want no part in such a family drama.

260
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,870
We're of the same kind.

261
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,509
A peaceful life isn't for us.

262
00:14:07,075 --> 00:14:09,316
An amazing journey is awaiting you.

263
00:14:09,325 --> 00:14:11,000
Why not set out now?

264
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:16,599
I'm going back to Shanghai tomorrow.

265
00:14:17,350 --> 00:14:18,230
If

266
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:19,831
you'd like to join me,

267
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,475
I'll be waiting for you at Peking Hotel.

268
00:14:23,775 --> 00:14:33,850
(Dates Restaurant)

269
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:47,119
Hello, Mr. Rong.

270
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:48,440
I'm Feng Shizhen,

271
00:14:48,719 --> 00:14:50,479
your children's new governess.

272
00:14:56,450 --> 00:14:58,930
Was it that I got my mother's look

273
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,200
that scared him?

274
00:15:01,950 --> 00:15:02,911
No way.

275
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:05,239
He can't be my father.

276
00:15:05,975 --> 00:15:08,415
Jiashang and I can't be siblings.

277
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,359
Trust me.

278
00:15:44,425 --> 00:15:46,265
I'll find out the truth for you.

279
00:16:26,025 --> 00:16:26,799
Hello.

280
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:29,460
Jiashang, it's me.

281
00:16:30,125 --> 00:16:31,280
I know.

282
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:33,319
Do you miss me?

283
00:16:34,625 --> 00:16:36,385
The temperature drops in Shanghai.

284
00:16:37,050 --> 00:16:38,290
Keep yourself warm.

285
00:16:38,325 --> 00:16:39,366
Don't catch a cold.

286
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,070
Got it.

287
00:16:43,125 --> 00:16:44,245
Have you had breakfast?

288
00:16:44,575 --> 00:16:45,475
Not yet.

289
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:47,840
I'm going to get

290
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,640
your favorite crab-roe buns

291
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:52,380
with wontons in clear soup

292
