398
00:22:36,350 --> 00:22:37,400
We all

399
00:22:37,475 --> 00:22:38,914
have our weaknesses,

400
00:22:40,225 --> 00:22:42,105
but you have to believe me

401
00:22:42,625 --> 00:22:44,064
that you can go a long way,

402
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:45,759
much longer

403
00:22:46,225 --> 00:22:47,666
than others, no doubt.

404
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:59,350
Forgive me if I overstep my bounds.

405
00:23:01,375 --> 00:23:05,296
Rong Jiashang is young,

406
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,350
capable

407
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:08,250
but

408
00:23:08,625 --> 00:23:10,225
also boyish,

409
00:23:10,950 --> 00:23:12,029
naive

410
00:23:12,029 --> 00:23:13,050
and lost.

411
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,825
Why do you adore him?

412
00:23:16,075 --> 00:23:18,834
