420
00:23:45,250 --> 00:23:46,970
Maybe

421
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:50,140
I'm the one that's naive and lost

422
00:23:50,575 --> 00:23:52,134
in love.

423
00:23:54,450 --> 00:23:55,770
You're right

424
00:23:56,250 --> 00:23:58,600
about Rong Jiashang.

425
00:23:59,375 --> 00:24:00,335
It's true

426
00:24:00,825 --> 00:24:02,106
that he's immature

427
00:24:02,475 --> 00:24:03,955
and less perfect

428
00:24:04,125 --> 00:24:05,246
than you,

429
00:24:06,275 --> 00:24:07,395
but

430
00:24:08,450 --> 00:24:09,570
he's growing

431
00:24:10,275 --> 00:24:11,395
and so am I.

432
00:24:13,925 --> 00:24:15,050
I think

433
00:24:16,625 --> 00:24:18,725
I'll enjoy this process.

434
00:24:20,425 --> 00:24:22,264
No matter how short it is,

435
00:24:24,025 --> 00:24:25,466
I won't regret

436
00:24:27,525 --> 00:24:29,084
